rules.description: Caps Lock to Escape on single press, Control on press and hold.
Use right_command+h/l to switch tabs in an application.
Use right_command+j/k to switch windows of the foreground application .
SpaceFN: Space+[hjkl] to Left, Down, Up, Right
SpaceFN: Space+b to Space (hold to repeat)
SpaceFN: m enter, p delete, comma backspace, u page up, n page down
SpaceFN: Call apps e browser, s d shell, f finder, c code, z slack
SpaceFN: Special french characters mapped over qwerty for nuphy air 75
Right command and e for [ and right command and r for ]
Right command and d for { and right command and f for }
Left option comma and period for <>
SpaceFN: Space+i to Home, Space+o to End
Use Return as Open and Use Fn+Return as Rename
Use Delete as Move to Trash
